      <title>拉马福萨称南非团结政府将继续存在</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/south-africa-s-unity-government-will-endure-ramaphosa-says-m10xzd0a</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨表示，南非十党联合政府将努力解决分歧并维持下去，因为该政府的垮台将削弱投资者信心并阻碍经济增长的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/south-africa-s-unity-government-will-endure-ramaphosa-says-m10xzd0a</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 16:37:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国淡化乌克兰使用远程导弹的传闻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/white-house-plays-down-talk-of-ukraine-using-long-range-missiles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫表示，美国总统乔·拜登在会见英国首相基尔·斯塔默时预计不会宣布改变针对乌克兰在俄罗斯境内使用远程导弹的政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/white-house-plays-down-talk-of-ukraine-using-long-range-missiles</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 16:26:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国钢铁价格飙升，因报道称交易决定可能在大选后做出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/us-steel-surges-on-report-deal-decision-may-come-after-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《华盛顿邮报》报道称，拜登总统不会立即阻止新日本制铁公司的收购要约，此后美国钢铁公司股价创下今年最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/us-steel-surges-on-report-deal-decision-may-come-after-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 16:25:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟财长避免前往布达佩斯，匈牙利哀叹抵制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/hungary-laments-boycott-after-eu-finance-chiefs-avoid-budapest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在匈牙利首都举行的财政部长会议上，主要参与者均未出席，此后匈牙利对欧盟的批评愈演愈烈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/hungary-laments-boycott-after-eu-finance-chiefs-avoid-budapest</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 16:01:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国称以色列袭击造成十年来首位西岸工人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/un-says-first-west-bank-worker-killed-in-decade-in-israeli-raid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国称，一名联合国工作人员周四在以色列的袭击中在约旦河西岸被杀，这是紧张局势升级十多年来联合国雇员首次在巴勒斯坦领土上遇害。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/un-says-first-west-bank-worker-killed-in-decade-in-israeli-raid</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 15:39:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟考虑延长制裁以解锁 500 亿美元乌克兰援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/eu-eyes-sanctions-extension-to-unlock-50-billion-in-ukraine-aid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟成员国审议了三项修改欧盟制裁制度的提案，旨在缓解美国的担忧，并启动一项向乌克兰提供 500 亿美元援助的计划，援助资金将由俄罗斯央行冻结的资产的利润提供。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/eu-eyes-sanctions-extension-to-unlock-50-billion-in-ukraine-aid</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 14:54:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>官员称普京可能加大破坏活动以回应英国在俄罗斯部署导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/putin-may-amp-up-sabotage-in-response-to-uk-missiles-in-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国和欧洲官员称，克里姆林宫威胁北约国家，因为乌克兰可能使用西方制造的导弹袭击俄罗斯的军事目标，这可能会采取增加破坏、网络和其他混合攻击的形式。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/putin-may-amp-up-sabotage-in-response-to-uk-missiles-in-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 14:53:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>荷兰威胁驱逐出境作为新庇护危机法的一部分</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/dutch-threaten-deportations-as-part-of-new-asylum-crisis-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[荷兰政府公布了该国有史以来最严格的移民政策，承诺加强边境管制，并威胁驱逐出境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/dutch-threaten-deportations-as-part-of-new-asylum-crisis-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 14:28:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基批评西方盟友在俄罗斯向库尔斯克附近推进时迟迟不提供援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/zelenskiy-blasts-western-allies-for-slow-aid-amid-russian-push-near-kursk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰领导人加大对西方伙伴支持力度不足的批评，同时声称乌克兰军队从上个月开始入侵俄罗斯，减缓了莫斯科在其他前线的进攻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/zelenskiy-blasts-western-allies-for-slow-aid-amid-russian-push-near-kursk</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 13:46:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普希望对美元叛逃者征收巨额关税，减少美国制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/trump-touts-a-mega-tariff-to-shield-dollar-cools-on-sanctions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普在其第一任总统任期内开创了使用关税作为治国武器的新方法。他承诺下次将全力以赴——甚至部署一个巨型版本来保护美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/trump-touts-a-mega-tariff-to-shield-dollar-cools-on-sanctions</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
